No. 15,

Misc.

Far East Conference et al. v. United States et al. John Milton and Elkan Turk for the Far East Conference et al.; and Josiah Stryker for the Isthmian Steamship Co., petitioners. Solicitor General Perlman, Assistant Attorney General Morison, ■Charles H. Weston and./. Roger -Wollenberg for the United States; and Francis S. Walker for the Federal Maritime Board, respondents.

United States District Court for the District of New Jersey. Motion for leave to file petition for writ of certiorari granted. Certiorari granted.

Mr. Justice Clark took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
